00:00:02.360 --> 00:00:06.180
The decade of 1960s is a politically and historically
fascinating decade, which in cross countries

00:00:06.180 --> 00:00:10.570
is prevalent while other protests to attain
the so promised great society.

00:00:10.570 --> 00:00:15.690
It is within this decade that clamored for
social change, liberation, and peace is at

00:00:15.690 --> 00:00:16.690
its height.

00:00:16.690 --> 00:00:22.080
It is also in the 60s when feminists strongly
advocate recognition of women�s right and

00:00:22.080 --> 00:00:24.830
status in the society.

00:00:24.830 --> 00:00:27.190
Philosophies and theories were also on the
rise.

00:00:27.190 --> 00:00:32.460
These streaks of events have perhaps strongly
influenced women�s fashion and makeup.

00:00:32.460 --> 00:00:37.739
This manifests that the swinging 60s hippie
fashion is strongly influenced by the swirl

00:00:37.739 --> 00:00:39.610
of events that happened over the decade.

00:00:39.610 --> 00:00:43.910
The 1960 is popularly known for the mod look.

00:00:43.910 --> 00:00:49.979
The mod look best describes the use of natural
colors for the lips, cheeks, and face.

00:00:49.979 --> 00:00:54.470
The accent is on the eyes which are painted
with pastel and cool colored eye shadows with

00:00:54.470 --> 00:00:57.440
shades of blue, green, and a bit of white.

00:00:57.440 --> 00:01:01.409
The eyes are also designed using thick mascaras
and dark eyeliners.

00:01:01.409 --> 00:01:04.610
The hairstyle also varies.

00:01:04.610 --> 00:01:09.040
The 1960s hairdo is influenced both by curl
and straight hairdo.

00:01:09.040 --> 00:01:14.000
The inclusion of small puffs on the side and
the top part of the head is a sophisticated

00:01:14.000 --> 00:01:15.000
modification.

00:01:15.000 --> 00:01:20.530
As for the fashion, the 1960s presents a diversity
of trends.

00:01:20.530 --> 00:01:27.010
It transgressed old fashion traditions and
dresses for women come in various lengths,

00:01:27.010 --> 00:01:31.480
designs, and colors. 1960s fashion range from
elegant covered up fashion to minis.

00:01:31.480 --> 00:01:37.370
The early 60s hippie fashion is characterized
by elegant dresses and pillbox hat.

00:01:37.370 --> 00:01:42.070
There are also the ball dresses with over-sized
buttons.

00:01:42.070 --> 00:01:46.960
Skirts and dresses at this time are at full
length.

00:01:46.960 --> 00:01:49.280
For these dresses, stiletto heeled shoes is
a fantastic addition.

00:01:49.280 --> 00:01:54.240
The mid 1960s slightly changed the 1960s fashion.

00:01:54.240 --> 00:01:59.450
It is in this quarter that miniskirts and
body hugging dresses were introduced.

00:01:59.450 --> 00:02:04.680
Style and elegance remained, but dresses were
trimmed with a lesser length.

00:02:04.680 --> 00:02:06.550
Skirts and dresses are in A-line shape.

00:02:06.550 --> 00:02:11.160
There is also a jump from covered up clothes
to sleeveless fashion.

00:02:11.160 --> 00:02:16.100
The mid 60�s hippie fashion style is largely
influenced by British designers.

00:02:16.100 --> 00:02:21.260
Young people love this fashion because it
feels more liberating and comfortable.

00:02:21.260 --> 00:02:26.770
The over-sized buttons were then replaced
by colorful and shimmering sequins, glossy

00:02:26.770 --> 00:02:28.700
fabrics, and bright colored fabrics.

00:02:28.700 --> 00:02:33.770
The use of lace was also highlighted through
the 1960s fashion.

00:02:33.770 --> 00:02:37.930
Hairstyle in the mid 1960s fashion also changed.

00:02:37.930 --> 00:02:41.320
Young people preferred shorter hairs let lose.

00:02:41.320 --> 00:02:46.240
Makeup or the mod look, however, remained
to be in style.

00:02:46.240 --> 00:02:51.140
For casual attires, women wear Capri trousers
and fluorescent colored clothes.

00:02:51.140 --> 00:02:56.380
The modern look of the mid 1960s fashion brings
about a playful side.

00:02:56.380 --> 00:03:01.420
This is why the 1960s fashion is highly patronized
and hippie to this date.

00:03:01.420 --> 00:03:08.320
The late 1960s fashion is characterized by
bell-bottomed trousers, vests, lounging pants

00:03:08.320 --> 00:03:10.540
or pajamas, and flowing caftans.

00:03:10.540 --> 00:03:17.380
Both men and women hover over shirts dyed
in vibrant colors of red, green, and yellow.

00:03:17.380 --> 00:03:21.890
Dresses at this time became more daring as
the tops appear haltered and midriff section

00:03:21.890 --> 00:03:22.980
slightly opened.

00:03:22.980 --> 00:03:28.630
The use of oversized belts animal skin leather,
animal prints, and fluorescent sleeveless

00:03:28.630 --> 00:03:29.900
shirts were also trendy.

00:03:29.900 --> 00:03:36.350
The highlight of the late 1960s fashion is
the use of colorful headbands, leather boots,

00:03:36.350 --> 00:03:38.540
vibrant sandals, and other accessories.

00:03:38.540 --> 00:03:43.489
For women, ankle bells and lockets are commonly
used.

00:03:43.489 --> 00:03:50.290
The late 1960s fashion also became controversial
as women began wearing haltered tops, braless.

00:03:50.290 --> 00:03:56.730
Hairstyle is straight, and long hair let lose,
accentuated by braids and headbands resembling

00:03:56.730 --> 00:03:58.710
the Native American look.

00:03:58.710 --> 00:04:02.290
For dresses, the waist lines are almost unnoticeable.

00:04:02.290 --> 00:04:07.880
This is in contrast with the fashion in the
early 1960's where dresses have tight waist.

00:04:07.880 --> 00:04:13.670
The 1960s fashion is truly controversial,
enticing and undying.

00:04:13.670 --> 00:04:20.269
Highly patronized is the 1960s fashion because
of its excellent color and design, and utmost

00:04:20.269 --> 00:04:21.269
comfort.

00:04:21.269 --> 00:04:27.970
Ladies who feel inspired by the 1960s fashion
can invest for a colorful wardrobe.

00:04:27.970 --> 00:04:32.710
Nowadays, it is easy to find haltered and
patched blouses online and on stores.

00:04:32.710 --> 00:04:39.280
If not, try to dye old shirts or put on colorful
patches to achieve the 1960s look.

00:04:39.280 --> 00:04:43.970
Match it up with colorful and flowery sandals
or shoes.

00:04:43.970 --> 00:04:49.260
Accessories may also be added to accomplish
a 1960s look.

00:04:49.260 --> 00:04:52.990
The 1960s fashion is great for teens and young
girls.

00:04:52.990 --> 00:04:56.669
The 1960s fashion can�t go without the mod
look.

00:04:56.669 --> 00:05:02.270
Despite the swinging 60s hippie fashion, the
mod look sustained its fame and patronage.

00:05:02.270 --> 00:05:08.780
Presently, both the 1960s fashion and makeup
inspire Hollywood artists and common people

00:05:08.780 --> 00:05:11.110
in setting up their wardrobe and makeup.

00:05:11.110 --> 00:05:16.210
To achieve the mod look, it is best to invest
in high quality make up.

00:05:16.210 --> 00:05:21.140
However, for the wardrobe, it is ideal to
reinvent old clothes.

00:05:21.140 --> 00:05:26.090
Simply match up colorful trousers and blouses
to feel the 60s fashion.

00:05:26.090 --> 00:05:30.561
It is not essential to spend for new clothes
because fashion trends changes from time to

00:05:30.561 --> 00:05:30.570
time.

